KEY for the TECHNIQUES LISTINGS
These apply to all the listings found in the links

TECHNIQUE
Self Explanatory, this is the name of the TECH
ACC
This is the Accuracy figure, Rated from Lowest to Highest - E, D, B, C, A, S
DMG
This is the Damage figure, Rated from Lowest to Highest - E, D, B, C, A, S
GuD
This is the GutsDown figure, Rated from Lowest to Highest - E, D, B, C, A, S
CRT
This is the Critical Hit figure, Rated from Lowest to Highest - E, D, B, C, A, S
GutC
This is the Guts Cost, or how much Guts you need to use the TECH, which will be reduced from your Guts Total
EFFECT
This is the main additional affect the TECH will have
CATER
This is the Catergory the TECH is in, either POWer or INTelligence
RANGE
This is range the attack can be used at
ELEMENT
This is an additional category for the TECH

KEY for the ADDITIONAL TECHNIQUES LISTINGS
These apply to all the listings found in the links, they apply to the second table given

TECHNIQUE
Self Explanatory, this is the name of the TECH
ACC
This is the Accuracy figure, the higher the number the better it is
DMG
This is the Damage figure, the higher the number the better it is
GuD
This is the GutsDown figure, the higher the number the more reduced from your opponent
CRT
This is the Critical Hit figure, the higher the number the greater the chance of a more damaging hit
CLS
This is the minimum CLASS you will get this TECH by SPARRING, you can get the Tech by Sparring in Higher Classes
SPAR
This is the AREA you will need to SPAR in
REQs
This is the required stats, the closer you are to this number, the more likely you will get the TECH

SPAR: - Any
Generally these are the default TECHs, in the cases you don't have them, you can gain it in any area of Sparring. The POWER stat seemed to produced the better probabilty to get the TECH, so I've listed it's requirement.
